Improved Tracker & Object Detector Effects (Refactor, Bug-Fixes, Enhancements)

commit.message: Update effects documentation related to parenting and needing a clip to be on a higher track to be visible.
Migrate child_clip_id for Tracker and Object Detector effects (if any) to utilize the Parent property of the clip instead
Bump version of OpenShot to 3.1.1-dev
Upgrade old Tracker and Object Detector JSON (<= OpenShot 3.1.1) to support fixed alpha and display_box_text properties.
Fix bug on undo/redo system with Tracked Object property edits
Fixed a few warnings in the RST documentation syntax (around code-blocks)

Do not show context menus for read-only properties, such as "visible" on a Tracked object. Improve documentation to notate new properties and read-only properties. Prevent a crash on video_widget.py if a load_json fails on the timeline.
Expanding the video and audio effect descriptions in documentation
Fix properties dock context menu, which was a regression that caused 2 menus to appear or options to be missing.
Fix undo/redo issues with Effects, due to data referencing in the Query class
Added class_filter context menu, to switch between available/visible classes on the ObjectDetection effect.

Refactor how we divide QMenu context menus on the Property Editor, to sub-divide into smaller lists (if needed). Also, change "Detected Objects" to "Tracked Objects" to be consistent between Parent and Selected Index menus.
Update documentation about 'Draw Box Text' and how it affects all tracked objects.
Sort tracked object properties correctly in property editor.
Update Tracker & Object Detector documentation
Removing "child_clip_id" property, no longer used for attaching clips to tracker effects: Use clip->Parent to attach clips to tracked objects now.

Fix property table view to correctly display choice context menus for Object detector selected objects. This was breaking due to the QIcon being NULL. Also, display the actual class name and object id for Object Detector selected objects choice menu.
Allow empty string in property model updating (i.e. so the user can clear class_filter in the Object Detector effect)
Fixing tooltips on webview timelines, and added "Parent" badge if a clip has a parent property set.
Disable process button on process effect dialog (Tracker effect, Object Detector effect)
Prompting user if Tracker effect region is invalid (i.e. not at the beginning of the clip), and then jumping the preview to the first frame.
